_sText: Hello... This is my first map.. Pretty shabby and it took me about a 2 days to make and edit (because those textures are crap) lol.. Umm I think you know the drill on how to install.. Well if you wanna know what I do is just put the map in the directory(s) of the folder just go to C:/Program Files/Steam/steamapps/<STEAM USERNAME>/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps so place the two files in the maps folder.. HAVE FUN :DDD!!
